  "elapsed_s": 191.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was one of the-- maybe last contribution of my mother to my destiny later on in my life, later on to buy-- to find and buy some little violin and start my lessons.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was when we returned back to Sofia, which was already three years later, three and a half years later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Vidin approximately until 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We remained there practically until the Red Army invaded Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans disappear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We understood-- there is something that I remember now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During these three years, what happened was one event in which some group of young people escape from the city, via water, river.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I understood that some of them succeed to reach Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how this happened, but they later on succeed to reach Palestine at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was-- the oldest daughter of one of them was the oldest daughter of my uncle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I understood that this was also group of-- a bigger group of young Jewish people that some of them that were catched were hanged and killed, but some of them succeed to reach Palestine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is how, after later on, is my relative from what I understood, become important political figure there at the time of the first governments of-- illegal government of Israel, before that Israel would become independent.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Margarita, the same like my grandmother of my mother's side, Margarita Cohen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] How I understood later on, she become a, a hero, her and her husband that she found there between after [? emigres ?] of young people of other countries that went through the same routes, risking their life.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, this happened there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
